headline: Fortis (FTS) Misses Q3 Earnings Estimates
summary: Fortis (FTS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -3.28% and +2.74%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
